   160έΗΤ## [12.1.0] (2024-05-18)
   161έΗΤ
   162έΗΤ### Added
   163έΗΤ
   164έΗΤ- auto-detect special node flags `node --eval` and `node --print` when call `.parse()` with no arguments ([#2164])
   166έΗΤ### Changed
   167έΗΤ
   168έΗΤ- prefix require of Node.js core modules with `node:` ([#2170])
   169έΗΤ- format source files with Prettier ([#2180])
   170έΗΤ- switch from StandardJS to directly calling ESLint for linting ([#2153])
   171έΗΤ- extend security support for previous major version of Commander ([#2150])
   173έΗΤ### Removed
   174έΗΤ
   175έΗΤ- removed unimplemented Option.fullDescription from TypeScript definition ([#2191])
   177έΗΤ## [12.0.0] (2024-02-03)
   178έΗΤ
   179έΗΤ### Added
   180έΗΤ
   181έΗΤ- `.addHelpOption()` as another way of configuring built-in help option ([#2006])
   182έΗΤ- `.helpCommand()` for configuring built-in help command ([#2087])
   184έΗΤ### Fixed
   185έΗΤ
   186έΗΤ- *Breaking:* use non-zero exit code when spawned executable subcommand terminates due to a signal ([#2023])
   187έΗΤ- *Breaking:* check `passThroughOptions` constraints when using `.addCommand` and throw if parent command does not have `.enablePositionalOptions()` enabled ([#1937])
   189έΗΤ### Changed
   190έΗΤ
   191έΗΤ- *Breaking:* Commander 12 requires Node.js v18 or higher ([#2027])
   192έΗΤ- *Breaking:* throw an error if add an option with a flag which is already in use ([#2055])
   193έΗΤ- *Breaking:* throw an error if add a command with name or alias which is already in use ([#2059])
   194έΗΤ- *Breaking:* throw error when calling `.storeOptionsAsProperties()` after setting an option value ([#1928])
   195έΗΤ- replace non-standard JSDoc of `@api private` with documented `@private` ([#1949])
   196έΗΤ- `.addHelpCommand()` now takes a Command (passing string or boolean still works as before but deprecated) ([#2087])
   197έΗΤ- refactor internal implementation of built-in help option ([#2006])
   198έΗΤ- refactor internal implementation of built-in help command ([#2087])
   200έΗΤ### Deprecated
   201έΗΤ
   202έΗΤ- `.addHelpCommand()` passing string or boolean (use `.helpCommand()` or pass a Command) ([#2087])
   204έΗΤ### Removed
   205έΗΤ
   206έΗΤ- *Breaking:* removed default export of a global Command instance from CommonJS (use the named `program` export instead) ([#2017])
   208έΗΤ### Migration Tips
   209έΗΤ
   210έΗΤ**global program**
