   234έΗΤ## [11.1.0] (2023-10-13)
   235έΗΤ
   236έΗΤ### Fixed
   237έΗΤ
   238έΗΤ- TypeScript: update `OptionValueSource` to allow any string, to match supported use of custom sources ([#1983])
