   405έΗΤ## [8.3.0] (2021-10-22)
   406έΗΤ
   407έΗΤ### Added
   408έΗΤ
   409έΗΤ- `.getOptionValueSource()` and `.setOptionValueWithSource()`, where expected values for source are one of 'default', 'env', 'config', 'cli' ([#1613])
   411έΗΤ### Deprecated
   412έΗΤ
   413έΗΤ- `.command('*')`, use default command instead ([#1612])
   414έΗΤ- `on('command:*')`, use `.showSuggestionAfterError()` instead ([#1612])
   416έΗΤ## [8.2.0] (2021-09-10)
   417έΗΤ
   418έΗΤ### Added
   419έΗΤ
   420έΗΤ- `.showSuggestionAfterError()` to show suggestions after unknown command or unknown option ([#1590])
   421έΗΤ- add `Option` support for values from environment variables using `.env()` ([#1587])
   423έΗΤ### Changed
   424έΗΤ
   425έΗΤ- show error for unknown global option before subcommand (rather than just help) ([#1590])
