   431έΗΤ## [8.1.0] (2021-07-27)
   432έΗΤ
   433έΗΤ### Added
   434έΗΤ
   435έΗΤ- `.copyInheritedSettings()` ([#1557])
   436έΗΤ- update Chinese translations of documentation for Commander v8 ([#1570])
   437έΗΤ- `Argument` methods for `.argRequired()` and `.argOptional()` ([#1567])
   439έΗΤ## [8.0.0] (2021-06-25)
   440έΗΤ
   441έΗΤ### Added
   442έΗΤ
   443έΗΤ- `.argument(name, description)` for adding command-arguments ([#1490])
   444έΗΤ  - supports default value for optional command-arguments ([#1508])
   445έΗΤ  - supports custom processing function ([#1508])
   446έΗΤ- `.createArgument()` factory method ([#1497])
   447έΗΤ- `.addArgument()` ([#1490])
   448έΗΤ- `Argument` supports `.choices()` ([#1525])
   449έΗΤ- `.showHelpAfterError()` to display full help or a custom message after an error ([#1534])
   450έΗΤ- `.hook()` with support for `'preAction'` and `'postAction'` callbacks ([#1514])
   451έΗΤ- client typing of `.opts()` return type using TypeScript generics ([#1539])
   452έΗΤ- the number of command-arguments is checked for programs without an action handler ([#1502])
   453έΗΤ- `.getOptionValue()` and `.setOptionValue()` ([#1521])
   455έΗΤ### Changed
   456έΗΤ
   457έΗΤ- refactor and simplify TypeScript declarations (with no default export) ([#1520])
   458έΗΤ- `.parseAsync()` is now declared as `async` ([#1513])
   459έΗΤ- *Breaking:* `Help` method `.visibleArguments()` returns array of `Argument` ([#1490])
   460έΗΤ- *Breaking:* Commander 8 requires Node.js 12 or higher ([#1500])
   461έΗΤ- *Breaking:* `CommanderError` code `commander.invalidOptionArgument` renamed `commander.invalidArgument` ([#1508])
   462έΗΤ- *Breaking:* TypeScript declaration for `.addTextHelp()` callback no longer allows result of `undefined`, now just `string` ([#1516])
   463έΗΤ- refactor `index.tab` into a file per class ([#1522])
   464έΗΤ- remove help suggestion from "unknown command" error message (see `.showHelpAfterError()`) ([#1534])
   465έΗΤ- `Command` property `.arg` initialised to empty array (was previously undefined) ([#1529])
   466έΗΤ- update dependencies
   468έΗΤ### Deprecated
   469έΗΤ
   470έΗΤ- second parameter of `cmd.description(desc, argDescriptions)` for adding argument descriptions ([#1490])
   471έΗΤ  - (use new `.argument(name, description)` instead)
   472έΗΤ- `InvalidOptionArgumentError` (replaced by `InvalidArgumentError`) ([#1508])
   474έΗΤ### Removed
   475έΗΤ
   476έΗΤ- *Breaking:* TypeScript declaration for default export of global `Command` object ([#1520])
   477έΗΤ  - (still available as named `program` export)
   479έΗΤ### Migration Tips
   480έΗΤ
   481έΗΤIf you have a simple program without an action handler, you will now get an error if
   482έΗΤthere are missing command-arguments.
