   522έΗΤ## [7.2.0] (2021-03-22)
   523έΗΤ
   524έΗΤ### Added
   525έΗΤ
   526έΗΤ- TypeScript typing for `parent` property on `Command` ([#1475])
   527έΗΤ- TypeScript typing for `.attributeName()` on `Option` ([#1483])
