   687έΗΤ## [6.2.0] (2020-10-25)
   688έΗΤ
   689έΗΤ### Added
   690έΗΤ
   691έΗΤ- added 'tsx' file extension for stand-alone executable subcommands ([#1368])
   692έΗΤ- documented second parameter to `.description()` to describe command arguments ([#1353])
   693έΗΤ- documentation of special cases with options taking varying numbers of option-arguments ([#1332])
   694έΗΤ- documentation for terminology ([#1361])
   696έΗΤ### Fixed
   697έΗΤ
   698έΗΤ- add missing TypeScript definition for `.addHelpCommand()' ([#1375])
   699έΗΤ- removed blank line after "Arguments:" in help, to match "Options:" and "Commands:" ([#1360])
