   906έΗΤ* removed deprecated `customFds` option from call to `child_process.spawn` ([#1052])
   907έΗΤ* rework TypeScript declarations to bring all types into imported namespace ([#1081])
   909έΗΤ### Migration Tips
   910έΗΤ
